data.description: This stunning Livingston Ranch residence boasting an open/split layout featuring 4 spacious bedrooms, 3 1/2 baths, a refreshing pool, relaxing spa, and fully paid solar system for energy efficiency. The property includes a separate AC unit in the garage, ensuring comfort and convenience. Nestled in a highly sought-after neighborhood, this home offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and eco-friendly amenities, promising an ideal living experience.  This home is move-in ready, and awaiting new owners!
